body_html:
I am only using the AAR, not building from source.
I am building with target SDK set to 24 and build tools on 24, due to a tool that only works with that setup.
My minSDK is set to 16.
Given it sounds like it's an AAR issue, I can try a build increasing the minSDK, but it was running at this level for some AR glasses.
